---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="FuryForm UI Kit Privacy" description="Privacy policy for the FuryForm UI Kit." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="container">
			<section class="page-intro">
				<p class="hero-eyebrow">Privacy</p>
				<h1>FuryForm UI Kit privacy policy</h1>
				<p>The FuryForm UI Kit is a design system asset package. It does not collect personal data by itself, but it is designed to support privacy-conscious form experiences.</p>
			</section>
			<section class="feature-block">
				<h2>What this covers</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>The UI Kit itself is static and client-side only.</li>
					<li>Data collection is controlled by the host application using the kit.</li>
					<li>Any form behavior should make privacy transparent to users.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			<section class="feature-block">
				<h2>When to use it</h2>
				<p>Use the UI Kit for product experiences where forms are shown clearly, labels are explicit, and user trust is prioritized.</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
